{"title":"EDA课程学习","uid":"3aa30f86d5e7a5fe52d49f283f39878f","slug":"EDA课程学习","date":"2021-11-29T10:31:08.000Z","updated":"2022-01-03T14:29:31.298Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/EDA课程学习.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h1 id=\"EDA课程学习\"><a href=\"#EDA课程学习\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"EDA课程学习\"></a>EDA课程学习</h1><p>这个篇博客主要是我在完成我的EDA课程在学习通上面的章节练习时，做的笔记。</p>\n<p>(这个脑图是老师提高的哈，非常耐撕！)</p>\n<img src=\"https://p.ananas.chaoxing.com/star3/origin/74a87b9c9f16977a49b56db94bed6e0b.png\" style=\"zoom: 100%;\" />\n\n<p>记忆宫殿</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">英文</th>\n<th align=\"center\">中文</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td align=\"center\">ISP</td>\n<td align=\"center\">在系统编程</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">LUT（Look-Up-Table）</td>\n<td align=\"center\">查找表</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">LAB</td>\n<td align=\"center\">逻辑阵列块</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">FPGA</td>\n<td align=\"center\">现场可编程逻辑门阵列</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">OTP</td>\n<td align=\"center\">一次性编程</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">PLD</td>\n<td align=\"center\">可编程逻辑器件</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">PROM</td>\n<td align=\"center\">只读存储器</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">PLL</td>\n<td align=\"center\">锁相环</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">ASIC</td>\n<td align=\"center\">专用集成电路</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">MC</th>\n<th align=\"center\">宏单元</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td align=\"center\">generate</td>\n<td align=\"center\">生成语句</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">HDL</td>\n<td align=\"center\">硬件描述语言</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">IP</td>\n<td align=\"center\">知识产权核</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">SRAM</td>\n<td align=\"center\">静态随机存储器</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">RTL</td>\n<td align=\"center\">寄存器传输级</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"></td>\n<td align=\"center\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"></td>\n<td align=\"center\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"></td>\n<td align=\"center\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"></td>\n<td align=\"center\"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<p>记忆点：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>STANDARD是默认打开的程序包</li>\n<li>CPLD 的基本功能模块    MC逻辑宏功单元</li>\n<li>在 VHDL 中,信号的数据传输是立即发生的</li>\n<li>CPLD通过可编程乘积项逻辑实现，基于与或阵列可编程</li>\n<li>综合的结果是不唯一的</li>\n<li>设计流程为:原理图/HDL 文本输入→功能仿真→综合→适配→时序仿真→编程下载→硬件测试。</li>\n<li>软 IP    提供用 VHDL 等硬件描述语言描述的功能块,但不涉及实现该功能块</li>\n<li>固 IP    以可执行文件的形式提交用户,完成了综合的功能块</li>\n<li>硬 IP     提供设计的最终产品掩膜</li>\n<li>仿真延时分为固有延时和仿真延时</li>\n<li>LUT 是存储在SRAM</li>\n<li>约束分别速度约束、面积约束、设计规则约束三种首先应满足速度约束</li>\n<li>适配器的功能是布局布线</li>\n<li>VHDL 的函数分为<strong>函数首</strong>和<strong>函数体</strong>两部分</li>\n<li>使用 LPM_ROM 实现一个 4 位乘法器（15×15）至少需要16*16个存储单元。 </li>\n</ul>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th></th>\n<th></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>PAL/GAL</td>\n<td>与阵列可编程，或阵列固定（1，0）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>PLA</td>\n<td>与阵列可编程或阵列可编程（1，1）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>PROM</td>\n<td>与阵列固定或阵列可编程（0，1）</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2 id=\"硬件结构与基本概念\"><a href=\"#硬件结构与基本概念\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"硬件结构与基本概念\"></a>硬件结构与基本概念</h2><h3 id=\"固有延时\"><a href=\"#固有延时\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"固有延时\"></a>固有延时</h3><p>固有延时也是惯性延时，是任何电子器件都存在的一种延时特性，主要物理机制是分布电容效应。固有延时需要考虑信号持续的时间，如果小于固有延迟，那么<strong>信号不会输出</strong>。</p>\n<h3 id=\"传输延时\"><a href=\"#传输延时\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"传输延时\"></a>传输延时</h3><p>传输延时：与固有延时相比，其不同之处在于传输延时时表达的是输入与输出之间的一种绝对延时关系。传输延时并不考虑信号持续的时间，它仅表示信号传输推迟或延迟了一个时间段，这个时间段即为传输延时。</p>\n<h3 id=\"CPLD的可编程是什么结构\"><a href=\"#CPLD的可编程是什么结构\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"CPLD的可编程是什么结构\"></a>CPLD的可编程是什么结构</h3><p>可编程的与阵列和固定的或阵列组成，即与或阵列可编程</p>\n<p>FPGA使用了一种可编程逻辑的形成方法，即可编程的查找表结构。</p>\n<h2 id=\"优化\"><a href=\"#优化\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"优化\"></a>优化</h2><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th></th>\n<th></th>\n<th></th>\n<th></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>速度优化</td>\n<td>流水线设计</td>\n<td>寄存器配平</td>\n<td>关键路径法</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>面积/资源优化</td>\n<td>串行化</td>\n<td>逻辑优化</td>\n<td>资源共享</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<p><img src=\"https://s4.ax1x.com/2021/12/28/TsVgHg.png\" alt=\"TsVgHg.png\"></p>\n<p>EDA软件开发流程</p>\n<p>综合-&gt;适配-&gt;配置（或者编程）</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>综合</th>\n<th>产生网表文件</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>适配</td>\n<td>将网表文件适配指定器件，产生最终的下载文件</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>配置（编程）</td>\n<td>将适配参数的下载文件，下载到目标器件，CPLD叫编程，FPGA叫做配置</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>仿真</td>\n<td>利用综合适配后产生的下载文件进行仿真</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h1 id=\"buffer：\"><a href=\"#buffer：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"buffer：\"></a>buffer：</h1><p>缓冲端口。它只允许内部回读输出的信号，即反馈。它的回读的信号是由内部产生、向外部输出的信号。</p>\n<h2 id=\"语句\"><a href=\"#语句\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"语句:\"></a>语句:</h2><p>顺序语句必须放到进程里面（<strong>PROCESS</strong>）</p>\n<h3 id=\"IF：（顺序）\"><a href=\"#IF：（顺序）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"IF：（顺序）\"></a>IF：（顺序）</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-vhdl\" data-language=\"vhdl\"><code class=\"language-vhdl\"><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token function\">rising_edge</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Clock<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">THEN</span>\n\t\t\tClk<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;=</span><span class=\"token operator\">NOT</span> Clk<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token keyword\">end</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"case-when：（顺序）\"><a href=\"#case-when：（顺序）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"case when：（顺序）\"></a>case when：（顺序）</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-vhdl\" data-language=\"vhdl\"><code class=\"language-vhdl\"><span class=\"token keyword\">case</span>\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>key<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\t<span class=\"token keyword\">is</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">when</span>\t<span class=\"token number\">'1'</span>\t<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\tled<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;=</span><span class=\"token number\">'1'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">when</span>\tother <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>led<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;=</span><span class=\"token number\">'0'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"when-else：（并行）\"><a href=\"#when-else：（并行）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"when else：（并行）\"></a>when else：（并行）</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-vhdl\" data-language=\"vhdl\"><code class=\"language-vhdl\">A<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;=</span><span class=\"token vhdl-vectors number\">\"111\"</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">WHEN</span> <span class=\"token function\">I</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">'1'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">ElSE</span>\n\t   <span class=\"token vhdl-vectors number\">\"110\"</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">WHEN</span> <span class=\"token function\">I</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">'1'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">ElSE</span>\n\t   <span class=\"token vhdl-vectors number\">\"101\"</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">WHEN</span> <span class=\"token function\">I</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">'1'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">ElSE</span>\n\t   <span class=\"token vhdl-vectors number\">\"100\"</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">WHEN</span> <span class=\"token function\">I</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">'1'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">ElSE</span>\n\t   <span class=\"token vhdl-vectors number\">\"011\"</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">WHEN</span> <span class=\"token function\">I</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">'1'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">ElSE</span>\n\t   <span class=\"token vhdl-vectors number\">\"010\"</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">WHEN</span> <span class=\"token function\">I</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">'1'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">ElSE</span>\n\t   <span class=\"token vhdl-vectors number\">\"001\"</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">WHEN</span> <span class=\"token function\">I</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">'1'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">ElSE</span>\n\t   <span class=\"token vhdl-vectors number\">\"000\"</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">WHEN</span> <span class=\"token function\">I</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">'1'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">ElSE</span>\n\t   <span class=\"token vhdl-vectors number\">\"111\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"状态机：\"><a href=\"#状态机：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"状态机：\"></a>状态机：</h3><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Moore摩尔</th>\n<th>输出取决于现态</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>Mealy<strong>米利</strong></td>\n<td>输出取决于现态和输入</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n","text":"EDA课程学习这个篇博客主要是我在完成我的EDA课程在学习通上面的章节练习时，做的笔记。 (这个脑图是老师提高的哈，非常耐撕！) 记忆宫殿 英文 中文 ISP 在系统编程 LUT（Look-Up-Table） 查找表 LAB 逻辑阵列块 FPGA 现场可编程逻辑门阵列 OTP 一...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.8k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"课程学习","slug":"课程学习","count":6,"path":"api/categories/课程学习.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"FPGA","slug":"FPGA","count":2,"path":"api/tags/FPGA.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#EDA%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">EDA课程学习</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%A1%AC%E4%BB%B6%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E4%B8%8E%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">硬件结构与基本概念</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%9B%BA%E6%9C%89%E5%BB%B6%E6%97%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">固有延时</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BC%A0%E8%BE%93%E5%BB%B6%E6%97%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">传输延时</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#CPLD%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%AF%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84\"><span class=\"toc-text\">CPLD的可编程是什么结构</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96\"><span class=\"toc-text\">优化</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#buffer%EF%BC%9A